         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">10 May [1859] ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ In acknowledging the receipt of yr letter dated 3rd Inst representing the insecurity of the bridge in the Botanic Gardens, ¶  I am directed by Mr Horne to inform you that as ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">59.05.10</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Balmain</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 59/1434, unit 3, p. 198, VPRS 975/P2 outward registered correspondence, VA 669 Department of Public Works, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">10 May [1859]<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In acknowledging the receipt of yr letter dated 3rd Inst representing the insecurity of the bridge in the Botanic Gardens,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to G. Horne, 3 May 1859.</p>
               </note> I am directed by Mr Horne to inform you that as there is no vote at his disposal for the erection of a new Bridge, it will be better, to prevent accident, to shut up the bridge until a vote can be obtained, and to post a notice to the effect that it is unsafe.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Sd T C Balmain</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The Director of Botanic Gardens</p>
         </div>
      </body>
